                "description": "This architecture supports creating a Secrets Manager private certificates engine within a Secrets Manager instance. The Secrets Manager private certificates engine enables you to issue and manage internal TLS/SSL certificates without relying on external Certificate Authorities. It supports creating and managing Root and Intermediate Certificate Authorities, defining Certificate Templates, and automating certificate issuance for internal applications and services."
